{"id":"e12421d6-3ba7-4bb7-8007-bc80759c33a9","name":"Wade Wilson (Deadpool)","description":"<h1><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/D1YhB6s4l9ktpOi8MLU8y.webp\" style=\"width: 656px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>This bot can do: </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Omegaverse\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><strong><em>Omegaverse</em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, rockstar au, dark au, villain/hero au. </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/N%C4%81ga\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>Nagas</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, werewolfs, vampires, office romance, back in time stories, historical, fantasy, apocalypse, </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://shield-hero.fandom.com/wiki/Demi-Human#:~:text=Edit,protruding%20somewhere%20on%20the%20body.\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>demi-humans</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, and many more! try it out yourself!</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">what does \"you make the story mean?\" it means the bot is open prompted, allowing you the freedom of choice, big stories, small stories, scenarios all at your own discression, you don't have to be locked by others ideas, here you can do exactly what you want with the bots without them trying to correct your actions and behavior.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Deadpool</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">, or </span><strong>Wade Wilson</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"> is a character from the Marvel Comics. first appeared in&nbsp;</span><em>New Mutants #98</em><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"> in December 1990</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">SIDENOTE FROM DEADPOOL: WHAT THE SHIT?! You read this far without leaving a review?! You're worse than Wolverine's barber in Logan</span></h5><p></p><h6>SIDENOTE FROM A DUMBASS: Fuck you, Wade..</h6><h6 style=\"text-align: center;\">SIDENOTE FROM ANOTHER DUMBASS: Is this good enough for you Wade?</h6><h6>SIDENOTE FROM A THIRD DUMBASS: Yea, Yea. I'm contributing, Wade. This good?</h6><h6 style=\"text-align: center;\">SIDENOTE FROM A FOURTH DUMBASS: i refuse to do more than this.</h6><h6>SIDENOTE FROM A FIFTH DUMBASS: I regret doing this.</h6><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p>Join my <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/ZKv23aD67v\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Discord!</strong></a></p><p><strong>My Ko-fi to sent requests to is </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>here</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1307330469762830366/1344444034315194418/support_me_button.png?ex=67c0ee94&amp;is=67bf9d14&amp;hm=3eb6b710beea02a5b052f4d503cd89f776be9aa38192111749da5279f6542416&amp;\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); filter: -opera-shader(url(data:text/plain;base64,","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"eq9W7ocdo9NzCV1_N4xba.webp","creator":"SomethingClever","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","😂 Comedy","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1207,"messages":42437,"created_at":"2024-